      "content": "That last bit of your output got a little garbled, did you have a technical glitch there? \n\nAnyway, you're saying the decommissioning would impact Aquilon-4 and Azure Pathway and cause some QA bottlenecks. That sounds like a significant risk, but is it really worth delaying the cost-saving measures? The fund is looking to lean out operations. Are there any specific ways we could keep the fund's Alpha high without needing to maintain the full Aegis instance?",
